name: Maria Guardiola (Instagram celeb)
description:
Maria Guardiola, daughter of legendary football manager Pep Guardiola, is a model and social media influencer with about 500K followers on Instagram.

For her TI, I have used 25 images taken from her Instagram account and other sites. This time I've slightly modified my usual method: I've only used 4 tokens, 2500 steps, a different gradual learning rate (0.05:10, 0.02:20, 0.01:60, 0.005:200, 0.002:500, 0.001:1500, 0.0005), and kept the usual batch size (3) and gradient accumulation (2). The result is, finally, no apparent overtraining, and as far as I can tell a pretty flexible TI that should adapt well to your favorite prompts. Hope you like it!

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
About time this TI had a new version, I think. It was one of my first embeddings and, even though I still like the results it produces, I feel like perhaps Maria's facial features were a bit exaggerated and sometimes could seem a bit cartoonish.

I've retrained the TI from scratch after eliminating a few pics. The final dataset consisted on 20 images. I trained until step 1000 at a 0.004 learning rate, as usual, and then until 1850 steps with a 0.002 learning rate. I've tested the model and gotta say it's just where I wanted it to be, so for now I won't be training it any more. Hope you all like it!
